DEVICE: Omi AI Wearable

FORM: Small circular disc, ~25mm diameter, ~15mm height
      Pebble/lens shape — domed top, flat bottom

OUTER SHELL: Matte metallic silver, fine sandblasted texture
             Subtle specular highlight on dome
             Thin dark horizontal groove around the middle equator

LED: Single small blue LED dot centered on top face
     Soft blue glow when active

CASE/HOLDER: Transparent frosted rubber ring (TPU)
             Wraps around the equator groove only
             Slightly wider than the shell — visible as a clear halo
             Small loop tab at top — eyelet for cord/chain threading

WEARABLE: Worn on a thin black rubber cord as a pendant

SIZE REFERENCE: Roughly the size of a large coat button
                Significantly smaller than a smartphone
                In meeting context: sits on desk, barely visible next to laptop
